1ab2258bcaaa48f1da161cbdfd35f40b9c2","tid":2256986,"uid":360800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19acca54766cda4f66fc97aab034043c033d9f7e","tid":2256986,"uid":166313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T20:39:26.000Z","msg":"There&rsquo;s cause and effect , but not karma"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T20:50:28.000Z","msg":"正如你所講，同立場。<br />\nkarma啊孽力啊我係唔信嘅。<br />\n<br />\n出世首抽奇爛無比嘅人少？<br />\n要怪罪所謂虛無飄渺嘅前世，何其blame the victim.<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界冇絕對公平，出世喺大富之家定妓女之家就已經開始有差別。<br />\n期待所謂公平嘅報應實在太傻。<br />\n呢個世界只有運動算係努力就必得回報之事。"},{"pid":"71d687f28d7da99c3af21c24f486e7d88aa2b800","tid":2256986,"uid":148245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T21:41:11.000Z","msg":"我比較相信共業，你種下嘅因，唔一定係你受番個果，可能係其他人受番個果。所以世人最好向善，減少共業"},{"pid":"e691d1b12c20b64fe03bb057e49a4941ba063d1c","tid":2256986,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T21:42:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd1b3b6202c5bc2f228339706338a0dbdd8c420c","tid":2256986,"uid":279927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T22:21:24.000Z","msg":"有因果報應 <br />\n只係時間問題<br />\n而且報應係以倍數報應<br />\n<br />\n當初都唔信有因果報應<br />\n人大左經歷多咗<br />\n事實係有因果報應"},{"pid":"fe473c2763cb1f7cfab135d99dc2f2024acd504c","tid":2256986,"uid":249708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T22:52:08.000Z","msg":"共產黨收皮未?<br />\n未? 冇囉咁咪"},{"pid":"0ff0130230c1412a65bb9024a196d522f4d82de7","tid":2256986,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T01:40:36.000Z","msg":"如果有，咁點解三萬隻咁高人工呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f3b7a79767e5b13c334553694ca4a40e7b36dd","tid":2256986,"uid":230293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0aa169c089efd1e11822d3fef9944cf3c3d6ac02","tid":2256986,"uid":212996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T19:29:35.000Z","msg":"有冇人相信因果報應呢一樣嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10